e":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"4487741468","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/4487741468","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvNDQ4Nzc0MTQ2OA==","status":"current","title":"Migrar Cardinal 3DS a Cybersource 3DS","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":156},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4487741468","tinyui":"/x/HIB9CwE","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4487741468","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4487741468/Migrar+Cardinal+3DS+a+Cybersource+3DS","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4487741468"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<blockquote local-id=\"2174dcbc-b8c0-42da-bd03-206e17a93abc\"><p local-id=\"8a8b2c06-fc3a-45c9-80aa-4c75b50613c0\" /><p local-id=\"8a8b2c06-fc3a-45c9-80aa-4c75b50613c0\">Setup Step es un paso nuevo que no tenemos en la implementaci&oacute;n de Cardinal 3DS. En este primer paso, se inicializa el proceso de 3DS, se averigua la marca de la tarjeta y se retornan par&aacute;metros necesarios para pasos futuros.<br /><br />En el orden de ejecuci&oacute;n, viene a reemplazar el getDdcJwt, al hacer lo mismo, pero adicionalmente proveyendo la formUrl para incorporar al ddcForm.</p></blockquote><p local-id=\"2e07b888-5504-47ce-ae7a-d353b93eb175\" /><h1 local-id=\"7d48844d-c48a-459b-8c46-3cd80b63273f\">Parametros de Request</h1><p local-id=\"9ece7654-16f1-4cfe-b93b-a480b7b93222\">PATH: /risk/v1/authentication-setups</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:local-id=\"cf3fc1b4-de64-4d92-9d21-43a3d265cd5a\" ac:macro-id=\"ebcf6731-70e0-453a-83db-f7952fbfbe55\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"breakoutMode\">wide</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"breakoutWidth\">760</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[{\"paymentInformation\": {\n    \"card\": {\n      \"type\": \"001\",\n      \"expirationMonth\": \"12\",\n      \"expirationYear\": \"2025\",\n      \"number\": \"4XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX\"\n    }\n  }\n}]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><ul local-id=\"99afe59b-4e8a-4ab5-a3e7-751a7820e45a\"><li local-id=\"9dcde778-ca22-4cf8-b531-76ece77c7b0d\"><p local-id=\"22f8675b-0b1a-4eba-9651-83b312e82d66\"><code>number</code> debe ser el visa token para VISA I?</p></li><li local-id=\"1c725394-099c-40cc-8b75-048d4df8af94\"><p local-id=\"d7a39aa0-b180-4b86-97fc-35ee7dc079e5\">c&oacute;mo se debe interpretar el valor de <code>type</code>? <a href=\"https://developer.cybersource.com/docs/cybs/en-us/api-fields/reference/all/rest/api-fields/payment-info-aa/payment-info-card-card-type.html\">Card Types Dictionary</a>. Podemos omitir.</p></li></ul><h1 local-id=\"cb1911e2-89f2-4882-a4cc-98932e272bd4\">Parametros de Response</h1><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:local-id=\"d6a0e9ea-e35a-4e57-b135-4f94d3359f93\" ac:macro-id=\"de9ed109-7869-4bca-9260-104ecf142573\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"breakoutMode\">wide</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"breakoutWidth\">760</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[{\n  \"clientReferenceInformation\": {\n    \"code\": \"1675295420285\",\n  },\n  \"consumerAuthenticationInformation\": {\n    \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJqdGkiOiIwYTFmZjNmYS02YTdiLTQ0NjYtYTgzOC04NTNjOTk2ZTMw\n                                   MDYiLCJpYXQiOjE2NzUyOTU0MjAsImlzcyI6IjVkZDgzYmYwMGU0MjNkMTQ5OGRjYmFjYSIsImV4cCI6MTY3NTI\n                                   5OTAyMCwiT3JnVW5pdElkIjoiNWI5YzRiYjNmZjYyNmIxMzQ0ODEwYTAxIiwiUmVmZXJlbmNlSWQiOiIzOTE2M\n                                   GMyZC1jMWU0LTQ0NjUtYWNlMy1lYjMyZDVhMWQ1NTkifQ.dl3w8s_ZpjA7kWmikyyYHO1Ak4TnzUHv8BuPra\n                                   tQukc\",\n    \"deviceDataCollectionUrl\": \"https://centinelapistag.cardinalcommerce.com/V1/Cruise/Collect\",\n    \"referenceId\": \"39160c2d-c1e4-4465-ace3-eb32d5a1d559\",\n    \"token\": \"AxizbwSTbhQQxCrDMCazABEBT9u+U5WYAXsQyaSZejFczCmAMAAAwAnp\"\n  },\n  \"id\": \"6752954202146024203955\",\n  \"status\": \"COMPLETED\",\n  \"submitTimeUtc\": \"2023-02-01T23:50:20Z\"\n}]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><ul local-id=\"fb4e7791-6657-4484-851b-6e2adb96172c\"><li local-id=\"128dec82-1bac-4d8a-ae34-922f3e9a7fbd\"><p local-id=\"15916c9c-d013-4f66-b7e9-462184b9c4f9\"><code>consumerAuthenticationInformation.accessToken</code> es el JWT token a colocar en ddcForm (Step 2)</p></li><li local-id=\"7eaac02a-9f2f-4275-b2f7-2f2fa6ac1238\"><p local-id=\"f9ed61a9-3693-4eaf-8468-a74420df7103\"><code>consumerAuthenticationInformation.deviceDataCollectionUrl</code> es la url a colocar en ddcForm (Step 2)</p></li><li local-id=\"f964be51-ef4f-4d83-9472-cc579d0598c8\"><p local-id=\"cf73e39b-9f22-4415-88aa-69763bfa9225\"><code>consumerAuthenticationInformation.referenceId</code> es el identificador que reemplaza a <code>session_id</code> al hacer el Payer Authentication Enrollment (Step 3 - ex LookUp)</p></li></ul><h1 local-id=\"dceaa8c1-4533-4280-8cbb-f8663b0d1075\">Desarrollo:</h1><ul local-id=\"625129f4-4171-43a9-9609-ae3df2ea73af\"><li local-id=\"4f2ce801-1654-4854-b93a-8f5ac9b66ca0\"><p local-id=\"9afc0647-197c-4141-89d8-46d69f085ac3\">Usando Direct API</p><ul local-id=\"d7d04e71-4311-4338-b8e5-2d985298e0af\"><li local-id=\"2d5c78b2-5ba1-45aa-a044-e9bfd7eb8957\"><p local-id=\"0db59391-c482-46a3-87e8-757d872891ae\">Para este endpoint se requiere un service completamente nuevo en external services</p></li><li local-id=\"7c58a133-6609-4c76-b7d8-c03a6de22493\"><p local-id=\"94bcafb2-29bc-42ed-9b8b-5d18b87a9f41\">Implementar en Vpos y Tpago la capa business que utiliza el external service</p></li></ul></li><li local-id=\"b2cdff45-b7d8-4734-b5b7-fb3e037f91ea\"><p local-id=\"b80c8026-4554-4084-a054-86b913b34aed\">Usando Ruby Gem</p><ul local-id=\"702382a7-0bd3-47d1-a261-57066b62fc48\"><li local-id=\"831bc85f-3252-4966-9c4f-35837e72c8f7\"><p local-id=\"315dcd4d-046e-45b1-b912-bd457cef7112\">Implementar en Vpos y Tpago la capa business que aproveche la gema de cybersource</p></li><li local-id=\"b2eee9b2-ba04-4ea8-b1e4-f5ef87168a4b\"><p local-id=\"9313a9fc-246c-4a3c-b7ce-b1fe7bfb983a\"><a href=\"https://github.com/CyberSource/cybersource-rest-samples-ruby/blob/master/Samples/PayerAuthentication/setup-completion-with-card-number.rb\">Setup con Card Number</a></p></li><li local-id=\"06d30b4d-35c5-4904-ad13-c7b6fada9f95\"><p local-id=\"aee26876-75d1-4613-8f59-43e4e66ccd0f\"><a href=\"https://github.com/CyberSource/cybersource-rest-samples-ruby/blob/master/Samples/PayerAuthentication/setup-completion-with-tokenized-card.rb\">Setup con Tokenized Card (VISA Token)</a></p></li></ul></li><li local-id=\"e528dfdd-d8ee-4a81-a70c-f60fce5c891d\"><p local-id=\"5c36217e-8c96-40c6-985c-8cfba3fe756d\">En Com&uacute;n</p><ul local-id=\"f817c158-0dd2-468f-84d9-6f7b5f9a2954\"><li local-id=\"858631bd-32eb-458c-8e17-896ad25df056\"><p local-id=\"bc53331f-dc8c-482f-9587-6126356005ad\">En vpos Portal y Tpago Portal, reemplazar la acci&oacute;n que genera el DDC JWT por esta, y actualizar la DDC form para recibir la formUrl y el JWT de este servicio</p></li><li local-id=\"625b57e3-c31a-443d-a44f-ac6c0803090a\"><p local-id=\"0b33c2f6-c02a-403f-b3cc-c77b3bda9264\">Se recomienda como best practice, disparar el proceso desde el javascript una vez se haya escrito la tarjeta completa, en lugar de esperar a que se de click en <code>Pagar</code>. Podr&iacute;amos disparar siempre que el string tenga 15+ numeros para cubrir todas las tarjetas conocidas (15-18 digitos)</p></li></ul></li></ul><p local-id=\"e086e6f5-dddb-412a-a71c-2f9b89ce6db0\" />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4488953858"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":339},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4488953858/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4488953858/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4488953858/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4488953858/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4488953858","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4488953858/STEP+1+-+Agregar+Setup+Step","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4488953858","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4488953858","tinyui":"/x/AgCQCwE","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}